  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Other Talk - Teaching Migration</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project aims to provide teachers, prospective teachers and teacher educators in Flanders with tools to teach their students (youngsters 12y-18y) to think critically about migration and refugees and to foster a media-wise attitude, so they are capable of better framing these topics in all their complexity. To achieve this aim, the project team will develop CPD e-learning pathways and an ITE course unit.</narrative>
  </description>
